{"word":"G3764 - οὐδέπω - oudépō - oo-dep'-o - As yet not","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">οὐδέπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">oudépō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">oo-dep'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">As yet not</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஒருக்காலும், இன்னும் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"not yet, not as yet"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3761 - οὐδέ - oudé - oo-deh'/3761\">G3761</a> and <a href=\"#/G4452 - -πω - -pō - po/4452\">G4452</a>; <i>not even yet:</i> - as yet not, never before (yet), (not) yet.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}